    "body": "Prepare to build the package index service, packages.spack.io, on Dockerhub.\r\n\r\nLocal build (in spack root dir):\r\n```\r\ndocker build -t spack/packages.spack.io:latest -f share/spack/docker/package-index/Dockerfile .\r\n```\r\n\r\nLocal test:\r\n```\r\ndocker run -p 8080:80 spack/packages.spack.io:latest\r\n```\r\n\r\n- [x] Removes leftover docker build stages from Travis CI.\r\n- [x] setup at https://cloud.docker.com/u/spack/repository/docker/spack/packages.spack.io/builds/edit\r\n\r\nFollow-up to #11665 and #11621",
